7. Ne2 is more usual here; I like this line, where I tempt black with the offer of a free pawn - 7. ... Qb6 8. O-O cd 9. cd NxP?! 10. NxN QxN 11. Nf3 with a natural attack.   I've played this line four times between here and over the board games, winning each time.
